  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《Age of Dark》is a turn-based strategy RPG.  Game Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Side-Scrolling Action Turn-Based Combat</strong><br>Each playable character’s skills and over 30 unique enemy types are brought to life with fluid pixel-art animations.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3673550/extras/0f7d8d7dc95ba53b08aec962734bbae8.avif?t=1747638975\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3673550/extras_big/0f7d8d7dc95ba53b08aec962734bbae8.avif?t=1747638975 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Path-point Exploration System</strong><br>Uncover secrets and navigate interconnected environments through a streamlined node-based progression.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Homage to Classic Exploration</strong><br>Inspired by <i>Ruina</i>, every scene is artfully presented in a hand-drawn map style, evoking a nostalgic yet fresh adventure.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3673550/extras/7b4f99abae9e49423420f58dae971959.avif?t=1747638975\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3673550/extras_big/7b4f99abae9e49423420f58dae971959.avif?t=1747638975 width=800 height=446 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《Age of Dark》is a turn-based strategy RPG.  Game Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Side-Scrolling Action Turn-Based Combat</strong><br>Each playable character’s skills and over 30 unique enemy types are brought to life with fluid pixel-art animations.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3673550/extras/0f7d8d7dc95ba53b08aec962734bbae8.avif?t=1747638975\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3673550/extras_big/0f7d8d7dc95ba53b08aec962734bbae8.avif?t=1747638975 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Path-point Exploration System</strong><br>Uncover secrets and navigate interconnected environments through a streamlined node-based progression.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Homage to Classic Exploration</strong><br>Inspired by <i>Ruina</i>, every scene is artfully presented in a hand-drawn map style, evoking a nostalgic yet fresh adventure.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3673550/extras/7b4f99abae9e49423420f58dae971959.avif?t=1747638975\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3673550/extras_big/7b4f99abae9e49423420f58dae971959.avif?t=1747638975 width=800 height=446 /></span></p>",
